quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  35,19,Bun…óo e yi'oowo fotataa
  35,20,wanaa ni…ìe …óen e ndaygu ngun
  35,21,wanaa …óowdi ndin e henndu wulndu ndun
  35,22,"Wanaa kadi wuur…ìe …ìen fotata e maay…ìe …ìen. Pellet, Alla no nanina on Mo O muuyani. Wanaa an [Nulaa…óo], woni naninoowo, won…ìe ka genaale …ìen"
  35,23,"An a wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo"
  35,24,"Pellet, Men nulirii ma goonga, ko a wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wanaa jertinoowo fe∆¥∆¥ii e ma…ì…ìe"
  35,25,"Si …ìe fennii ma, hari adinoo…ìe …ìe …ìen fenniino (Nulaa…ìe mun), fewndo …ìen Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe addannoo …ìanngannduyeeji, e ∆äeri e Deftere ndayginoore"
  35,26,Refti nanngitir mi yeddu…ìe …ìen (halakuyee). Taskii no lepte An …óen wa…ótinirnoo
  35,27,"E a tinaali wonnde Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Men fu…óiniri …óam dim…óe seertu…óe noone. Hino ka pelle, …óate daneeje e bo…óeeje seertyu…óe noone, e pete …ìaleeje"
  35,28,"Hino e yim…ìe …ìen, e daabeeji …óin, e neemoraa…ói …óin, …ói nooneeji mun kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko hulata Alla e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, ko anndu…ìe …ìen. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo, Haforoowo"
  35,29,"∆Åen janngoo…ìe Deftere Alla nden, …ìe √±ii…ìi e julde, …ìe nafqii ko Men arsiki …ìe kon gunndoo e kene, hi…ìe jortii njulaaku ngu sontataa"
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana …ìe njo…ìdiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin, O …ìeyda …ìe e …ìural Makko ngal. Kanko, ko O Haforoowo, Annditanoowo [on]"
